yingyinNormal.zh: 个人资料？个人资料被存放在哪里？

yingyinNormal.en: There's no way. The guy's too high profile.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不可能，那个人地位太显著了。

yingyinNormal.en: Good for you, isn't it? Quite a high profile client.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对你是好事吧？好厉害的客户。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, have you finished writing your profile yet? Almost.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，你的交友信息写完了吗? 快了。

yingyinNormal.en: Nice juicy excerpt, profile on Thomas Yates, his literary comeback.
yingyinNormal.zh: 精彩的选节，托马斯·耶茨的深度报道，他的文学回归。

yingyinNormal.en: So, Bert, you were telling us how you updated your profile?
yingyinNormal.zh: 伯特，你刚说到你更新了自己的个人档案？

yingyinNormal.en: Benji, we are trying to keep a low profile. You want drama, go to the opera.
yingyinNormal.zh: 班吉，我们都要努力保持低调，你想来点刺激的剧情，去看歌剧吧。

yingyinNormal.en: What about installing the security profile? Well. That's gonna be like a minute tops.
yingyinNormal.zh: 替换安全资料的时间呢？这个用最多一分钟。

yingyinNormal.en: What's our profile on Moryakov? We have our agent who's been assigned to him, sir. Jim?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们对莫里科夫有什么了解？我们有特工调查过他，先生。吉姆？

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. So, to get the ledger, one of us needs to enter the torus and change the security profile.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，所以，要想拿到账册，必须有一个人进入那个圆环体替换掉其中安全资料。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't forget, she has a national profile after the Walker investigation. Truth and justice personified.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别忘了在沃克案调查后，她在全国也有点名气了，真理和正义的化身。

yingyinNormal.en: That's nice. I haven't had much success meeting people online. I didn't either, until I revamped my profile.
yingyinNormal.zh: 挺好的，我在网络交友这方面还从未成功过。我也是，直到我修改了我的个人档案。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't worry about him. Alright. All he has to do is install the fake profile before I get to the gait analysis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别担心他，好吗？他只要在我进入步态分析之前，把伪造的档案导入就行了。

yingyinNormal.en: Is makeup really necessary? When someone looks at your dating profile, the first thing they see is your picture.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真有必要化妆吗? 当然，当有人浏览你的交友信息时，第一眼看的就是你的照片。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the first time we're hiring senior interns, so some of our intern questions may not exactly fit your profile.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是我们第一次聘用老年实习生，所以我们面试的问题可能有些不符合你的简历。

yingyinNormal.en: Now Jexica was a success. So delete Jexica and put up your real profile and let everybody like you before it's too late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 杰克西卡成功了。在还来得及之前，删掉杰克西卡放上你的真实信息，让大家喜欢你。

yingyinNormal.en: When this profile came out about everything the general just mentioned, the White House said that he was politicizing terrorism.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这篇详细阐述了将军刚刚所说的内容的专访发行后，白宫竟然指责他利用恐怖主义做政治文章。

yingyinNormal.en: Electrical conduit? Bottom line is, there's no way into that terminal unless your profile is pre-installed in the security system.
yingyinNormal.zh: 电缆导管呢？这是底线。要想进入终端，除非把你的个人资料提前存入安全系统。

yingyinNormal.en: So there are all these questions for your profile that you can answer if you want to or not. Like religious views, political views, people who inspire you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些关于你个人资料的问题，你可以选择填，也可以不填，比如宗教观，政治观，你钦佩的人。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: They do a great deal more than fill hotel bedrooms and bring in high-<highlight>profile</highlight> arts events and good press for a year.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们做了很多，不仅仅是让酒店爆满、举办关注度高的艺术活动以及带来高质量的新闻报道。

examination_example.sentence: It's not that people's <highlight>profiles</highlight> are dishonest, says Catalina Toma of Wisconsin-Madison University,"but they portray an idealised version of themselves."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 威斯康星-麦迪逊大学的卡特琳娜·托马说，并不是人们的个人形象是不真诚的，“而是他们描绘了一个理想化的自己。”

examination_example.sentence: It's no surprise that high-<highlight>profile</highlight> athletes can influence children's eating behaviors.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这并不奇怪，高知名度的运动员可以影响孩子们的饮食行为。

examination_example.sentence: The technology press conferences have been <highlight>high-profile</highlight> in the past.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科技新闻发布会过去一直备受瞩目。

examination_example.sentence: There is an increase of just one percent from the previous year despite a year of <highlight>high-profile</highlight> launches.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然高调宣传了一年，但是比例也只比去年增加了1%。

examination_example.sentence: It reduces our curiosity by showing us exactly what we already want, based on our <highlight>profiles</highlight> and preferences.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它会根据我们的个人资料和偏好向我们展示我们已经想要的东西，从而降低我们的好奇心。
它的形象确实得到了提升。

examination_example.sentence: But a passing reference in a recent <highlight>profile</highlight> by Glamour magazine to her 20-hour workdays prompted an outpouring of admiration.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但在《魅力》杂志最近的一篇简介中，她不经意地提到了每天工作20小时，这引起了人们对她的的钦佩之情。

examination_example.sentence: In addition, our site's unique (独特的) features for members include <highlight>profile</highlight> pages, discussion forums (论坛), and other contents.
